Package commInfra

Class Message

java.lang.Object
commInfra.Message
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Message
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
This class defines the constructors of the various messages that the clients and servers exchange between them in a Distributed solution for the Airport Problem . The communication is based in message exchanges of type Message in a TCP channel.
